        <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-blue-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0">▶</span><span><strong>VIZ</strong> (15 pts) — pairs V with Z for a powerful 3-letter play</span></li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-blue-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0">▶</span><span><strong>VOW</strong> (9 pts), <strong>VIM</strong> (8 pts), <strong>VAN</strong> (6 pts) — solid 3-letter options when premium tiles aren't available</span></li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-blue-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0">▶</span><span><strong>VAV</strong> (9 pts) — uses both V tiles if you're unlucky enough to draw them together</span></li>
